<title>Yesu Yana Son Mutane Y2</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Yesu yana son mutane,
 Duk mutanen duniya,
 Baƙi, fari, ko kuwa ja,
 Yana ƙaunar dukansun.
 Yesu yana son mutanen duniya.

[V2]
 Yesu yana ƙaunar yara,
 Dukan yaran duniya,
 Baƙi, fari, ko kuwa ja,
 Duka ɗaya wurinsa,
 Yesu yana ƙaunar yaran duniya.</lyrics>
</song>